arStrings.szText: We know you're a friend of the deserter. Our spies have seen the two of you together.
Calculating, cruel, and on a petty power trip
I don't know who you mean. I'm a merchant, I sell fish to everyone in Gea Kul.
Your lies are tedious. I hoped I would not need to shed blood today.
Please! I swear I don't know anything, I'm a faithful member of the church!
(sigh) I knew this was a waste of time. Should have just done as Osric suggested and killed you straight away.
